Package: cltools
Type: Package
Title: A Collection of Data Wrangling Tools for Statistical Researchers
Version: 0.9.2
Author: Oliver Hawkins
Maintainer: Oliver Hawkins <oli@olihawkins.com>
Description: A collection of data wrangling tools for statistical researchers.
    This packages provides simple ways to perform common data wrangling tasks, 
    such as creating column and row totals, column and row percentages,
    statisitcal indices, and deflated series.
